name: Secret Robohead Campsite
description:
This huge robot was found buried into the hills and lost inside the forest. The curious townsfolk went inside its head and cleaned up all the rusted cables and wiring. Later on they turned it into a secret little campsite. Now both people from and town and afar come here during the camping season to discover this giant enigma resting silently in the ground.

Secret Hunters! See if you can find:
- a toaster
- a lizzard
- the Swampgirl
- a Vuvuzela Plant
- a little bird
- a creepy human shaped bush
